y muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/228d0ba34d1a50784da5e3efec3f1700.poster.avif?t=1683006074\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/228d0ba34d1a50784da5e3efec3f1700.webm?t=1683006074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/228d0ba34d1a50784da5e3efec3f1700.mp4?t=1683006074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Beat up your foes through turn-based combat and master the timing of action commands throughout combat to enhance both your offense and defense! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/ea27420e030a41c819fdf28e1cd14a3b.avif?t=1683006074\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/73c2d9f198a484e537c4f60315fd49fc.poster.avif?t=1683006074\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/73c2d9f198a484e537c4f60315fd49fc.webm?t=1683006074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/73c2d9f198a484e537c4f60315fd49fc.mp4?t=1683006074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defend weakened companions during enemy attacks with other companions to help them last longer in fights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327360/extras/2a31cf771a61813e080688f0df4c1e27.avif?t=1683006074\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Exploring, talking to inhabitants, and winning fights gives companions ideas on new abilities and 